        <name>setupShiftRegisterPins</name>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Initialize all 74HC595 shift register control pins. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Sets all shift register pins to OUTPUT mode and initializes them to safe states. Clears the shift register on startup to ensure a known state. This function should be called once during system initialization. <simplesect kind="note"><para>Must be called before any shift register operations </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
