    <briefdescription>
<para>Shift register control logic for 28Cx EEPROM programmer. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Contains functions for setting up and controlling the shift register. This includes pin initialization and any low-level control functions needed to interface with the shift register. </para>
